quran[7{c,v,t}:
9,123,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, jung karo unn munkareen haq se jo tum se qareeb hain aur chahiye ke woh tumahray andar sakhti payen, aur jaan lau ke Allah Muttaqiyun ke sath hai"
9,124,"jab koi nai sourat nazil hoti hai to un mein se baaz log ( mazaq ke tor par musalmanoon se ) puchhte hain ke"" kaho, tum mein se kis ke imaan mein is se izafah howa ?"" ( is ka jawab yeh hai ke ) jo log imaan laaye hain un ke imaan mein to fi al waqea ( har nazil honay wali sourat ne ) izafah hi kya hai aur woh is se dilshaad hain"
9,125,Albata jin logon ke dilon ko ( nifaq ka ) rog laga howa tha unn ki sabiq najasat par ( har nai sourat ne ) aik aur najasat ka izafah kar diya aur woh martay dam taq kufar hi mein mubtala rahay
9,126,kya yeh log dekhte nahi ke har saal aik do martaba yeh azmaish mein daaley jatay hain? magar iss par bhi nah tauba karte hain nah koi sabaq letay hain
9,127,"jab koi sourat nazil hoti hai to yeh log aankhon hi aankhon mein aik dosray se baatein karte hain ke kahin koi tum ko dekh to nahi raha hai, phir chupkay se nikal bhagtay hain Allah ne un ke dil phair diye hain kyunkay yeh nasamajh log hain"
9,128,"dekho! tum logon ke paas aik rasool aaya hai jo khud tum hi mein se hai, tumhara nuqsaan mein parna is par shaq hai, tumhari Falah ka woh harees hai, imaan laane walon ke liye woh shafeeq aur Raheem hai"
9,129,"ab agar yeh log tum se mun phertey hain to ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kehdo ke"" mere liye Allah bas karta hai, koi mabood nahi magar woh, usi par mein ne bharosa kya aur woh maalik hai arsh azeem ka """
